4:
Ladies and gentlemen! Are you
ready for a special, summertime
performance?!
6:
Give it up for our undefeated arena
beauty—Shiiining Eclair!
9:
Thanks for coming, everybody!
Now... Let me show you just how
brilliantly the summer shines!
17:
The winner is... Eclair! A round of
applause for our champion!
19:
Now then... I have a very important
announcement to make.
21:
Starting tomorrow, Eclair will be
taking a summer vacation—in other
words, she will NOT be performing at
the coliseum!
24: But fear not, my loyal fans!
29:
We're currently in the middle of
creating a special feature about
yours truly—directed by our very
own Platinum Legends!
32:
Thaaat's right, folks! We'll be
following our champ here as she
enjoys her vacation! Get ready to
see a side of her that you've never
seen before!
35:
Be on the lookout for "Passionate
Platinum!" Coming soon!
42: Sorry for the wait, you two!
50:
Thank you. I had a feeling you'd like
it, which is why I picked it.
55:
Alright, Eclair. Anything you'd like to
say before you start your vacation?
59:
In interview mode already, are we?
Well...
62:
I intend to make the most of this
frankly gorgeous destination.
66:
Thank you so much for inviting me. 
I know I'm in good hands with you
here as my interviewers.
70:
Talk about pressure... You sure we're
the right people for the job?
74:
Like I said, if I'm going to be followed
around on vacation, I'd at least like
the crew to be people I'm familiar
with.
77:
That's why I asked you two. You don't
need to be nervous. Just act natural.
82:
I see. So instead of interviewers, we
should act as your friends.
89:
What's more natural than going on
a vacation with your friends? We're
going to have the time of our lives!
93: First stop: the ocean! Let's go!
102:
Yeah... This is definitely going in the
feature.
107:
Hey, Stella, is that camera
waterproof?
112:
That it is. Even seawater will do it no
harm.
116:
Great, then there's no reason you
can't join us! Come here!
120:
Leave it to Eclair to draw all this
attention.
125:
Well, what could possibly draw more
attention than me?
129:
How can you say that with a straight
face?
134:
Hehe... I'm only joking. I'm actually
quite flattered. Who knew I'd be just
as eye-catching on other worlds?
138:
You there. Is there something you'd
like to say?
141:
Y-yes... Please join our beach
volleyball tournament!
143:
Those chiseled muscles, those
limber legs! I must see your
beauty—I mean, your athleticism in
action!
146:
What a passionate proposal. All
right. I accept.
149:
R-really?! Then right this way! The
match is about to start!
160:
That's the game! Victory goes to the
A team!
162:
That speed! Those movements! 
And above all else... That BEAUTY! 
Who is she?!
168:
I've come to enjoy this summery
destination, so try to remember that
name until the seasons change,
okay?
179:
Thank you. I was surprised by how
much fun I had.
182:
Although... I may have gone a little
overboard at the end there.
187:
So what? You really gave everyone
a show.
190:
That volleyball match was insane!
Can I get your autograph?!
194:
I don't see why not! Does anyone
have a pen?
197:
Ah, hello. I was wondering when
you'd approach me.
200:
You've been watching me since my
little romp through the ocean, after
all.
203:
M-Miss Eclair, could I do a feature on
you? Please?!
205:
Ah, where are my manners! 
My name is Gina, and I'm with Paradise
Isle's tourism department! 
Here, my card!
208:
Magazine editor, huh... I'm guessing
that's where this feature would be
published, correct?
211:
That's right! Having someone like
you here will surely help us promote
this island!
213:
I understand that you're already in
the middle of another project, but
please allow me to join you on your
vacation as well!
217:
Looks like I've just been
double-booked. Welcome aboard,
Gina.
220:
Th-thank you so much! You won't
regret this!
223:
If there is anyone else who wishes to
join us, by all means! The summer
season has just begun!
227:
We'll make this a summer to
remember!
